<bibRefCitation id="EFD2D282FFCEFFEFFCCB9EB0FBCE02A8" author="Irwin, H. S. &amp; Barneby, R. C." box="[791,1076,195,217]" pageId="4" pageNumber="190" pagination="1 - 454" refId="ref5268" refString="Irwin, H. S. &amp; Barneby, R. C. (1982) The American Cassiinae: A synoptical revision of Leguminosae tribe Cassieae subtribe Cassiinae in the New World. Memoirs of the New York Botanical Garden 35: 1 - 454." type="journal article" year="1982">Irwin &amp; Barneby (1982: 498)</bibRefCitation>
